high_descs: take a turn and go to the countertop.
pick up the knife that is in front of the microwave.
Take the knife and go over to the apple.
Open the apple under the sink and then cut it in couple of pieces.
Put the knife in the sink.
pick up a piece of the apple.
look around the room then pick up a piece of the apple from the bowl.
Put the apple in the bowl that is in the sink.
turn around and look at the bowl on the other side of the room.
turn back to the countertop.
Put the bowl on the countertop in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Getting a piece of apple and putting it in the bowl on the countertop.

high_descs: Head to the kitchen countertop on the right.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left to reach the apple.
Cut the apple in the sink with the knife.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Move right to face the bowl in the sink.
Put the apple slice in the bowl in the sink.
Pick up the bowl from the sink.
Turn right to reach the countertop in front of the microwave.
Put the bowl on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the Bowl with the Apple slice from the CounterTop.

high_descs: Go left towards the wall, then turn right to approach the countertop in the kitchen area.
Pick up the knife from the counter to the right of the sink.
Approach the apple to the left of where you got the knife.
Open the cabinet beneath the sink and slice the apple inside the sink.
Place the knife inside the sink.
Pick up one apple slice from the sink and close the cabinet.
Look down to the bowl in the sink.
Open the cabinet beneath the sink and place the apple inside the bowl on the sink.
Pick up the bowl with the apple slice in it and shut the cabinet.
Go to the countertop to the right of the sink.
Place the bowl down on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Slice an Apple, place one slice in a Bowl, and place that Bowl on a CounterTop.
